  },
  {
    icon: '🧠',
    title: 'Semantic Memory',
    desc: 'Agents learn from every run. Vector-based memory with auto-injection. Your team gets smarter over time.',
  },
  {
    icon: '🔌',
    title: '12+ Model Adapters',
    desc: 'Claude, Gemini, Codex, Ollama, AWS Bedrock, Azure OpenAI, GCP Vertex, and more. Use any model, anywhere.',
  },
  {
    icon: '🖥️',
    title: 'Desktop + Web + CLI',
